# Economy Fabric 


An Economy API for Fabric.

![https://i.imgur.com/ZQ835CK.png](https://i.imgur.com/ZQ835CK.png) 


### Gradle dependency 


```
repositories {
    maven { url 'https://pisaiah.com/maven-repo/' }
}
```
```
dependencies {
    compileOnly "me.isaiah.mods:EconomyFabric:1.4"
}
```

Just place this mod into your mods folder.
